description:
Get ready for Party Fever,
a new downloadable content pack for Party Party Time!
Enjoy 10 brand new minigames!
Invite your friends and keep the party going!

The Party Fever Pack includes the following content:

10 New Minigames:
6 Competitive Games
- Tower Tumble
- Watch the Water
- Panel Drop
- Not too Far!
- Head to Head Rock-Paper-Scissors
- Memory Survival
4 Co-op Games
- Train Track Traveler
- Rope Jump
- Block Breaker
- Robot Defense
name: Party Fever Pack
